Package model

Class Movie

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Movie
  • public class Movie
extends java.lang.Object
    Movie object that contains movie details. Also contains ArrayList<Review> of reviews for the movie, and an ArrayList<Showtime> of Showtime objects for this movie. Also contains average ratings left by reviewers.
    Since:
    2019-11-09
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Lim Wai Leong, Oh Jun Teng, Edhie Wahidin Michelle, Myat Hmu Khin
